        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple 錢包數碼車匙功能，將支援歐洲三車廠新舊車款</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/16/apple-wallet-digital-car-key-audi-volvo-polestar/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-wallet-digital-car-key-audi-volvo-polestar</link>
