            <title>彭博：AirPods 內置紅外線相機開發中 　預計 2026 年量產、可與 Vision Pro 互動</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/apple-planning-smart-glasses-and-airpods-with-cameras-for-2027/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-planning-smart-glasses-and-airpods-with-cameras-for-2027</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/apple-planning-smart-glasses-and-airpods-with-cameras-for-2027/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:30:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動音樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple AirPods]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1269419</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Mark Gurman 在彭博專欄表示，Apple 計劃於 2026 年推出一款內置紅外線相機的 AirPods。在 Apple 不斷推進 AR 發展的潮流下，新 AirPods 有望改變無線耳機市場，與擴增實境（AR）技術無縫結合，提升用户互動體驗。專家預計這款 AirPods 將於 2026 年開始大規模量產。</p><p>外媒《Tech EDT》引述知名 Apple 分析師郭明錤指，Apple 計劃在新 AirPods 加入紅外線鏡頭，有望與 Apple Vision Pro 等 AR 裝置生態系統深度整合，為用户提供全新的使用感受。雖然尚未有具體影像處理功能的規格，但可以預期新 AirPods 可以監察用家環境變化，讓用家利用更多手勢操作，與 Vision Pro 等 AR 裝置交流。</p><p>至於 Apple Smart Glasses，市場消息指出，Apple 計劃於 2027 年推出這款 AR 眼鏡。這些眼鏡將配備高整合度的 AR 技術，並能與 Apple 裝置深度協作，使擴增實境技術更貼近日常生活。儘管這款產品的具體規格尚未有詳細公佈，但其潛在功能已引起了市場的期待。</p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://macdailynews.com/2024/10/14/apple-smart-glasses-and-airpods-with-cameras-could-launch-in-2027/">Mac Daily</a>、<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/10/14/apple-smart-glasses-airpods-cameras-2027/">Mac Rumors</a>、<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/09/29/apple-vision-pro-future-ar-glasses">9to5Mac</a>、<a href="https://www.techedt.com/apple-to-begin-mass-production-of-airpods-with-cameras-by-2026?fbclid=IwY2xjawF7MDpleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZsqxquM7bifnYebx7ycLv6tc66fJ9if6JOJZgFkquMmsKqFASwOq9nq8A_aem_Fb0h_CXvgOG7Th6f6pU7WQ">Tech EDT</a>、<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-13/apple-smart-home-plans-new-os-smart-displays-vision-pro-integration-robots-m27kw5m7">Bloomberg</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/17/airpods-4-review/mobile-music/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】AirPods 4 最新主動降噪版，降噪效能比 Pro 更強 + 音質超靚重低音強勁</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/08/airpods-have-charging-cable/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">AirPods 耳機盒內竟有充電線　台網民：驚天大發現</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/24/apple-discontinues-the-iphone-15-pro-iphone-13/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">三款 iPhone 官網下架，三款 AirPods 同時停售</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/apple-planning-smart-glasses-and-airpods-with-cameras-for-2027/mobile-music/headphones/">彭博：AirPods 內置紅外線相機開發中 　預計 2026 年量產、可與 Vision Pro 互動</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
